How to Use

0. Link webcam to your machine

1. Prepare the CMake build environment

2. Clone the project to local
$ git clone git@github.com:browny/hand-tracking.git
$ cd hand-tracking

3. Take out-of-source CMake build
$ mkdir release
$ cd release
$ cmake ..
$ make

4. Enjoy
$ cd bin
$ ./main

5. Exit
Press 'Esc' to close window and quit
